{"tid":2307353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私隱公署： 林卓廷查冊後踢爆方國珊的選舉開支 方國珊反投訴成立 需要刪除片段","createTime":"2020-12-01T06:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T06:37:18.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9815ba06ce2fcb29f4b23bc356f63c20487ddf","tid":2307353,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"林卓廷日前收到私隱專員公署的信件，指接獲方國珊投訴，該名捐贈者遭「起底」滋擾，公署同時質疑他查册的目的違反《土地註冊條例》，要求他移除當日記者會片段，否則會調查。林卓廷強調不會删除片段，又批評公署剝削公眾知情權。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷查冊　被私隱專員公署質疑目的違法<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414950&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414950%26refer%3DShare&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0vkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=72113339\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414950%26refer%3DShare&h=a331fa6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414950&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"9b6eed11c9afe8492b54a0d11ebad79d50e3c07b","tid":2307353,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}